text: Barbara Mensing is an German archer. She was born on 23 September 1960. Mensing competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Barbara MensingBarbara MENSING == References == Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:German archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for Germany Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Germany Category:Sportspeople from North Rhine-Westphalia
